{
  "video_id": "Bs86giWcjLA",
  "title": "Why must artists be poor? | Hadi Eldebek",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12920.0,
      "end_time": 15496.0,
      "text": "I come from a family of five brothers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15520.0,
      "end_time": 17240.0,
      "text": "all scientists and engineers."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18000.0,
      "end_time": 21000.0,
      "text": "A few years ago, I sent them the following email:"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22920.0,
      "end_time": 26536.0,
      "text": "\"Dear brothers, I hope this message finds you well."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26560.0,
      "end_time": 28695.0,
      "text": "I am emailing to let you know"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28720.0,
      "end_time": 31855.0,
      "text": "that I'm dropping out of my master's program in engineering"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31880.0,
      "end_time": 34680.0,
      "text": "to pursue a career as a full-time musician."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 35480.0,
      "end_time": 38519.0,
      "text": "All that I ask from you is not to worry about me.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 40360.0,
      "end_time": 42400.0,
      "text": "Brother number one replied."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 42760.0,
      "end_time": 44759.0,
      "text": "He was encouraging but a bit skeptical."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 45560.0,
      "end_time": 47696.0,
      "text": "He said, \"I wish you the best of luck."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 47720.0,
      "end_time": 49560.0,
      "text": "You're going to need it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 49800.0,
      "end_time": 51455.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 51480.0,
      "end_time": 54360.0,
      "text": "Brother number two was a little bit more skeptical."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 55400.0,
      "end_time": 56775.0,
      "text": "He said, \"Don't do it!"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 56800.0,
      "end_time": 59775.0,
      "text": "This will be the worst mistake of your life."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 59800.0,
      "end_time": 61256.0,
      "text": "Find a real career.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 61280.0,
      "end_time": 62856.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 62880.0,
      "end_time": 67696.0,
      "text": "Well, the rest of my brothers were so enthusiastic about my decision,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 67720.0,
      "end_time": 69456.0,
      "text": "they didn't even respond."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 69480.0,
      "end_time": 72216.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 72240.0,
      "end_time": 75416.0,
      "text": "I know that the skepticism coming from my brothers"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 75440.0,
      "end_time": 77495.0,
      "text": "is out of care and concern for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 77519.0,
      "end_time": 78936.0,
      "text": "They were worried."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 78960.0,
      "end_time": 82496.0,
      "text": "They thought it would be difficult to make it as an artist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 82520.0,
      "end_time": 85150.0,
      "text": "that it will be a challenge."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 85400.0,
      "end_time": 87280.0,
      "text": "And you know what? They were right."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 88240.0,
      "end_time": 90976.0,
      "text": "It is such a challenge to be a full-time artist."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 91000.0,
      "end_time": 94376.0,
      "text": "I have so many friends who need to have a second job"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 94400.0,
      "end_time": 96616.0,
      "text": "as a plan B in order to pay for the bills,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 96640.0,
      "end_time": 100440.0,
      "text": "except that plan B sometimes becomes their plan A."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 101920.0,
      "end_time": 105216.0,
      "text": "And it's not just my friends and I who experience this."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 105240.0,
      "end_time": 110175.0,
      "text": "The US Census Bureau states that only 10 percent of art school graduates"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 110200.0,
      "end_time": 113296.0,
      "text": "end up working as full-time artists."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 113320.0,
      "end_time": 115776.0,
      "text": "The other 90 percent, they change careers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 115800.0,
      "end_time": 119520.0,
      "text": "they work in marketing, sales, education and other fields."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 120160.0,
      "end_time": 122616.0,
      "text": "But this is not news, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 122640.0,
      "end_time": 126400.0,
      "text": "We almost expect the artist to be a struggling artist."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 126960.0,
      "end_time": 128799.0,
      "text": "But why should we expect that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 130680.0,
      "end_time": 132936.0,
      "text": "I read an article in the \"Huffington Post\""
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 132960.0,
      "end_time": 135976.0,
      "text": "saying that four years ago, the European Union"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 136000.0,
      "end_time": 139496.0,
      "text": "began the world's largest ever arts funding initiative."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 139520.0,
      "end_time": 143136.0,
      "text": "Creative Europe will give 2.4 billion dollars"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 143160.0,
      "end_time": 145840.0,
      "text": "to over 300,000 artists."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 146520.0,
      "end_time": 151976.0,
      "text": "In contrast, the US budget for our National Endowment for the Arts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 152000.0,
      "end_time": 155936.0,
      "text": "the largest single funder for the arts across the United States,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 155960.0,
      "end_time": 159776.0,
      "text": "is merely 146 million dollars."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 159800.0,
      "end_time": 161936.0,
      "text": "To put things into perspective,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 161960.0,
      "end_time": 166960.0,
      "text": "the US budget for the military marching bands alone"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 166120.0,
      "end_time": 169480.0,
      "text": "is almost twice as much as the entire NEA."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 171560.0,
      "end_time": 176960.0,
      "text": "Another striking image comes from Brendan McMahon for the \"Huffington Post,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 176120.0,
      "end_time": 179216.0,
      "text": "saying that out of the one trillion dollar budget"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 179240.0,
      "end_time": 182560.0,
      "text": "for military and defense-related spending,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 182800.0,
      "end_time": 186456.0,
      "text": "if only 0.05 percent were allocated to the arts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 186480.0,
      "end_time": 190775.0,
      "text": "we would be able to pay for 20 full-time symphony orchestras"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 190800.0,
      "end_time": 192816.0,
      "text": "at 20 million dollars apiece,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 192840.0,
      "end_time": 196296.0,
      "text": "and give over 80,000 artists"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 196320.0,
      "end_time": 199400.0,
      "text": "an annual salary of 50,000 dollars each."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 200200.0,
      "end_time": 203456.0,
      "text": "If that's only 0.05 percent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 203480.0,
      "end_time": 205440.0,
      "text": "imagine what a full one percent could do."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 206920.0,
      "end_time": 209616.0,
      "text": "Now, I know we live in a capitalist society,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 209640.0,
      "end_time": 211720.0,
      "text": "and profits matter a lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 212760.0,
      "end_time": 215600.0,
      "text": "So let's look at it from a financial angle, shall we?"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 216280.0,
      "end_time": 218656.0,
      "text": "The US nonprofit arts industry"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 218680.0,
      "end_time": 224496.0,
      "text": "generates more than 166 billion dollars in economic activity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 224520.0,
      "end_time": 228160.0,
      "text": "it employs 5.7 million people"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 228400.0,
      "end_time": 230976.0,
      "text": "and it returns 12.6 billion dollars"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 231000.0,
      "end_time": 232576.0,
      "text": "in tax revenue."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 232600.0,
      "end_time": 234856.0,
      "text": "But this is only a financial angle, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 234880.0,
      "end_time": 239376.0,
      "text": "We all know that the arts is way more than just an economic value."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 239400.0,
      "end_time": 241496.0,
      "text": "The arts brings meaning to life."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 241520.0,
      "end_time": 243480.0,
      "text": "It's the spirit of our culture."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 244480.0,
      "end_time": 246935.0,
      "text": "It brings people together and it supports creativity"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 246960.0,
      "end_time": 248720.0,
      "text": "and social cohesion."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 249360.0,
      "end_time": 253456.0,
      "text": "But if the arts contributes this much to our economy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 253480.0,
      "end_time": 257599.0,
      "text": "why then do we still invest so little in arts and artists?"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 259120.0,
      "end_time": 263576.0,
      "text": "Why do more than 80 percent of our schools nationwide"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 263600.0,
      "end_time": 267000.0,
      "text": "still experience budget cuts in arts education programs?"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 268360.0,
      "end_time": 271960.0,
      "text": "What is it about the value of arts and artists"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 271120.0,
      "end_time": 273000.0,
      "text": "that we still don't understand?"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 274790.0,
      "end_time": 277776.0,
      "text": "I believe the system is flawed and far from being fair,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 277800.0,
      "end_time": 279936.0,
      "text": "and I want to help change that."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 279960.0,
      "end_time": 281976.0,
      "text": "I want to live in a society"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 282000.0,
      "end_time": 283696.0,
      "text": "where artists are more valued"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 283720.0,
      "end_time": 286376.0,
      "text": "and have more cultural and financial support"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 286400.0,
      "end_time": 290416.0,
      "text": "so they can focus on creating arts instead of being forced to drive Ubers"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 290440.0,
      "end_time": 293120.0,
      "text": "or take corporate jobs they'd rather not have."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 293880.0,
      "end_time": 297376.0,
      "text": "There are other sources of income for artists, however."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 297400.0,
      "end_time": 299655.0,
      "text": "There are private foundations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 299680.0,
      "end_time": 302256.0,
      "text": "grants and patrons who give money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 302280.0,
      "end_time": 307950.0,
      "text": "except a vast majority of artists don't know about these opportunities."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 307120.0,
      "end_time": 310736.0,
      "text": "On one side you have institutions and people with money."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 310760.0,
      "end_time": 313376.0,
      "text": "On the other side you have artists seeking funding,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 313400.0,
      "end_time": 316215.0,
      "text": "but the artists don't know about the people with the money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 316240.0,
      "end_time": 318696.0,
      "text": "and the people with the money don't necessarily know"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 318720.0,
      "end_time": 320960.0,
      "text": "about the artists out there."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 320120.0,
      "end_time": 323816.0,
      "text": "This is why I am very excited to share \"Grantpa,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 323840.0,
      "end_time": 326775.0,
      "text": "an online platform that uses technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 326800.0,
      "end_time": 330376.0,
      "text": "to match artists with grants and funding opportunities"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 330400.0,
      "end_time": 334150.0,
      "text": "in a way that is easy, fast and less intimidating."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 334400.0,
      "end_time": 338536.0,
      "text": "Grantpa is only one step towards solving an existing problem"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 338560.0,
      "end_time": 340400.0,
      "text": "of funding inequality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 341200.0,
      "end_time": 344455.0,
      "text": "but we need to work collectively on multiple fronts"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 344480.0,
      "end_time": 347800.0,
      "text": "to reevaluate how we view the artists in our society."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 348560.0,
      "end_time": 352000.0,
      "text": "Do we think of arts as a luxury or a necessity?"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 352920.0,
      "end_time": 357560.0,
      "text": "Do we understand what goes on in the day-to-day life of an artist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 357800.0,
      "end_time": 361336.0,
      "text": "or do we still believe that artists, no matter how struggling they are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 361360.0,
      "end_time": 364480.0,
      "text": "are happy simply because they're following their passion?"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 366320.0,
      "end_time": 370360.0,
      "text": "In a few years, I plan to send my brothers the following email:"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 372120.0,
      "end_time": 375400.0,
      "text": "\"Dear brothers, I hope this message finds you well."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 376200.0,
      "end_time": 379135.0,
      "text": "I am emailing to let you know that I am doing great"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 379160.0,
      "end_time": 381656.0,
      "text": "and so are hundreds of thousands of artists"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 381680.0,
      "end_time": 385176.0,
      "text": "who are being valued more culturally and financially"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 385200.0,
      "end_time": 388216.0,
      "text": "and getting enough funding to focus on their crafts"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 388240.0,
      "end_time": 390256.0,
      "text": "and create more art."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 390280.0,
      "end_time": 392575.0,
      "text": "I appreciate all of your support."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 392600.0,
      "end_time": 394536.0,
      "text": "Couldn't have done it without you.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 394560.0,
      "end_time": 395776.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 395800.0,
      "end_time": 399880.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}